00:00:59.252 --> 00:01:01.493
Madam Liu, you have a cold constitution.

00:01:02.500 --> 00:01:04.290
A few doses should help
warm your body up.

00:01:04.550 --> 00:01:06.470
It won't affect
your chances of having children.

00:01:07.613 --> 00:01:08.292
Thank you.

00:01:27.372 --> 00:01:28.693
Master Liu, your pulse…

00:01:30.773 --> 00:01:31.812
Be frank.

00:01:36.012 --> 00:01:38.790
It's a condition of innate weakness
in the vital essence of the kidneys.

00:01:38.812 --> 00:01:39.493
You may

00:01:40.773 --> 00:01:42.413
never have children in this lifetime.

00:01:43.053 --> 00:01:44.133
Nonsense!

00:01:46.253 --> 00:01:47.693
I already have a son.

00:01:50.053 --> 00:01:50.890
Please calm yourself.

00:01:51.572 --> 00:01:53.452
A pulse doesn't lie.

00:01:53.973 --> 00:01:56.053
If you once had a child,

00:01:56.452 --> 00:01:57.092
then…

00:01:58.173 --> 00:02:00.173
it must have been a stroke of chance.

00:02:02.253 --> 00:02:02.973
What did you say?

00:02:03.812 --> 00:02:04.773
Say it again.

00:02:06.812 --> 00:02:09.013
I wouldn't dare speak carelessly.

00:02:12.070 --> 00:02:13.400
They call this the "Wilted Glory."

00:02:13.412 --> 00:02:14.310
Take it for seven days,

00:02:14.733 --> 00:02:16.013
and even a healthy young man

00:02:16.200 --> 00:02:17.890
will have a pulse
as weak as rotting wood.

00:02:18.030 --> 00:02:19.790
Not even the most
highly skilled physician

00:02:19.972 --> 00:02:21.573
can detect otherwise.

00:02:36.700 --> 00:02:39.412
