00:04:26.493 --> 00:04:27.533
Liu Qinghe!

00:04:28.012 --> 00:04:29.213
Liu Qinghe!

00:04:30.093 --> 00:04:31.772
Liu Qinghe!

00:04:33.012 --> 00:04:35.533
He's your own flesh and blood!

00:04:36.772 --> 00:04:39.812
Why are you doing this?

00:04:40.012 --> 00:04:41.550
- Why?
- An illegitimate child doesn't deserve

00:04:41.932 --> 00:04:44.213
a place in the Liu ancestral tomb.

00:04:46.372 --> 00:04:47.413
You wretch.

00:04:48.173 --> 00:04:50.372
