00:05:02.053 --> 00:05:02.572
Wenyu!

00:05:03.372 --> 00:05:04.012
Wenyu!

00:05:04.932 --> 00:05:05.653
Wenyu!

00:05:05.692 --> 00:05:06.572
Hold her down.

00:05:07.190 --> 00:05:09.590
Let her watch with her own eyes
as that wretched son of hers

00:05:09.853 --> 00:05:11.093
